This repository contains drivers for the MIDAS data acquisition system

Website: https://midas.triumf.ca

low-level drivers:
	  * operation of CAEN V1742 waveform digitisers

high/level drivers:
	  * operation and interrupt driven triggering of Struck SIS 3100 VME 
	    interface, interrupt handling is done in a separate thread
	  * easy operation of CAEN V1742 waveform digitisers